 
<p>
Filipinos, including expats, are buying lots of copies of the book
<em><a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/16/asia/philippines-marcos-books-truth-rewrite-history-intl-hnk-dst/index.html">Marcos Martial Law: Never Again</a></em>, fearing that the new president, son
of the late dictator Marcos, will suppress the memory of his crimes.

 